OL,4,GBoth the main public service
OL,5,Gbroadcasters are celebrating big
OL,6,Gbirthdays. The BBC is marking its
OL,7,Gcentenary just as Channel 4 turns 40.
OL,9,FThere are certain parallels.
OL,11,FBoth face a degree of uncertainty about
OL,12,Ftheir future and finding the right way
OL,13,Fto mark the occasions may not have been
OL,14,Feasy.
OL,16,FThe BBC's centenary had seemed an
OL,17,Funderstated affair until now. A raft of
OL,18,Fspecial programmes over the past week
OL,19,Fhave played to its core audience.
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
