OL,4,FAnd just what should be celebrated? The
OL,5,FBBC as it is today? Its rich heritage?
OL,6,FOr its humble origins on Savoy Hill.
OL,8,FActually the three are interlinked. The
OL,9,Fbasic values of the organisation go all
OL,10,Fthe way back to 1922 and its early
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FAll its major services have a rich
OL,14,Fheritage to tap into but any
OL,15,Forganisation which stays still or lives
OL,16,Foff its past becomes a museum piece
OL,17,Feventually.
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
OL,22,                                   G3/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
