OL,4,FIt's been interesting to see the use of
OL,5,Fa common ident for the anniversary
OL,6,Facross different channels. Again this
OL,7,Fsuggests each service is part of
OL,8,Fsomething bigger.
OL,10,FOver at Channel 4, the celebrations
OL,11,Fhave seemed more muted.
OL,13,FA revival of Friday Night Live was a
OL,14,Freminder of one part of its special
OL,15,Fpersonality. No doubt Countdown will be
OL,16,Fmarking its own 40th in style. (There
OL,17,Fwill be a little 40th birthday surprise
OL,18,Ffor Pres fans before Countdown on
OL,19,FWednesday.)
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
