PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1668985221
OL,4,FPart of the channel's core audience
OL,5,Ftoday might regard a 40-year-old as
OL,6,Fover-the-hill.
OL,8,FAnother part of the public knows all
OL,9,Ftoo well that so many of the serious,
OL,10,Fchallenging programmes and minority
OL,11,Finterests which also ran through its
OL,12,FDNA are now seen less frequently.
OL,14,FWill there be any revival of the
OL,15,Foriginal idents? Well frankly reviving
OL,16,Fthe blocks has less of an impact now as
OL,17,Fit has happened so often.
OL,19,FMore seriously both organisations face
OL,20,Funcertain futures.
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
