OL,4,FSome opponents of privatisation had
OL,5,Fhoped that the plan would be shelved
OL,6,Funder Liz Truss. However during the
OL,7,Fsummer leadership contest Rishi Sunak
OL,8,Factively supported it. Watch this
OL,9,Fspace.
OL,11,FAs for the BBC, its celebrations are a
OL,12,Freminder that its core audience might
OL,13,Fbe prepared to fight for it. Any big
OL,14,Fdecisions won't come this side of the
OL,15,Fnext General Election.
OL,17,FBut anyone thinking radical thoughts
OL,18,Fmight be advised to look at the
OL,19,Faudience response to some of the
OL,20,Fcelebratory programmes.
